title: #92Noon Live from TCO! Wobby/Warren/Leber/Boudreau/Birk/Softy
description: 92Noon is back once again at TCO Performance Center! Wobby swings by to start the show, Vikings COO Kevin Warren shares his thoughts on football and family, Ben Leber calls in to talk Vikings-Seahawks, Wild head coach Bruce Boudreau calls in from Calgary, Matt Birk makes his regular appearance and Dave "Softy" Mahler from AM 950 KJR in Seattle shares the adversarial perspective!
